  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Empowering the Niger Border Police (Directorate of Territorial Surveillance) Headquarters and Regional Partners</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project seeks to enhance the Directorate of Territorial Surveillance capacities to have a stronger internal management and improve public perception in order to increase Nigerian national police credibility, attraction, respect of ethics, and efficiency. This will be realized through supporting the restructuring and reassertion of the mandate of this directorate, as well as exchanging best practices among G5 Sahel neighboring countries, thus contributing to the implementation of stronger and more coherent border management strategies.</narrative>
  </description>
